I think Lilio and his friends
will become fine salvagers
like Rex in the future.

rows.label: tlk006501_07_msg0002
rows.name:
A veteran salvager like me is saying
it, so there's no doubt about it.

rows.label: tlk006501_07_msg0003

I mean, even though I've only let
them use Normal Cylinders, they're
bringing back Divine Beast Quartz.

rows.label: tlk006501_07_msg0005
rows.name:
Well, they do get a ton of Krabbles
and Lysaats following them, so they're
always getting injured, though.
